#: content/hig/_index.md:18
msgid "Design Vision"
msgstr "Vizija oblikovanja"

#: content/hig/_index.md:21
msgid ""
"KDE's design vision focuses on two attributes of KDE software that connect "
"its future to its history:"
msgstr ""
"Vizija oblikovanja KDE se osredotoča na dva atributa programske opreme KDE, "
"ki povezujeta njeno prihodnost z njeno zgodovino:"

#: content/hig/_index.md:24
msgid "Simple by default..."
msgstr "Privzeto enostaven ..."

#: content/hig/_index.md:26
msgid ""
"*Simple and inviting. KDE software is pleasant to experience and easy to use."
"*"
msgstr ""
"*Preprosto in vabljivo. Programska oprema KDE je prijetna za izkušnjo in "
"enostavna za uporabo.*"

#: content/hig/_index.md:29
msgid ""
"**Make it easy to focus on what matters** --- Remove or minimize elements "
"not crucial to the primary or main task. Use spacing to keep things "
"organized. Use color to draw attention. Reveal additional information or "
"optional functions only when needed."
msgstr ""
"**Poskrbite za lažje osredotočanje na tisto, kar je pomembno** --- "
"Odstranite ali zmanjšajte elemente, ki niso ključni za primarno ali glavno "
"nalogo. Uporabite razmik, če želite, da so stvari organizirane. Uporabite "
"barvo, da bi pritegnili pozornost. Razkrijte dodatne informacije ali izbirne "
"funkcije le, če je to potrebno."

#: content/hig/_index.md:33
msgid ""
"**I know how to do that!** --- Make things easier to learn by reusing design "
"patterns from other applications. Other applications that use good design "
"are a precedent to follow."
msgstr ""
"**Vem, kako to storiti!** --- Olajšajte učenje s ponovno uporabo vzorcev "
"oblikovanja iz drugih aplikacij. Druge aplikacije, ki uporabljajo dobro "
"zasnovo, so vzori, ki jih velja spremljati."

#: content/hig/_index.md:36
msgid ""
"**Do the heavy lifting for me** --- Make complex tasks simple. Make novices "
"feel like experts. Create ways in which your users can naturally feel "
"empowered by your software."
msgstr ""
"**Opravi težka opravila v mojem imenu** --- Naredite zapletene naloge "
"preproste. Naj se začetniki počutijo kot strokovnjaki. Ustvarite načine, ob "
"katerih se lahko vaši uporabniki naravno počutijo opolnomočeni s svojo "
"programsko opremo."

#: content/hig/_index.md:40
msgid "...Powerful when needed"
msgstr "... Zmogljiv, kadar je to potrebno"

#: content/hig/_index.md:42
msgid ""
"*Power and flexibility. KDE software allows users to be effortlessly "
"creative and efficiently productive.*"
msgstr ""
"*Moč in prilagodljivost. Programska oprema KDE uporabnikom omogoča, da so "
"brez napora ustvarjalni in učinkovito produktivni.*"

#: content/hig/_index.md:45
msgid ""
"**Solve a problem** --- Identify and make very clear to the user what need "
"is addressed and how."
msgstr ""
"**Rešite težavo** --- Identificirajte in uporabniku zelo jasno povejte, "
"katero potrebo ste naslovili in kako."

#: content/hig/_index.md:47
msgid ""
"**Always in control** --- It should always be clear what can be done, what "
"is currently happening, and what has just happened. The user should never "
"feel at the mercy of the tool. Give the user the final say."
msgstr ""
"**Vedno v nadzoru** --- Vedno bi moralo biti jasno, kaj lahko naredi, kaj se "
"trenutno dogaja in kaj se je pravkar zgodilo. Uporabnik ne sme biti nikoli "
"prepuščen na milost orodju. Dajte uporabniku zadnjo besedo."

#: content/hig/_index.md:51
msgid ""
"**Be flexible** --- Provide sensible defaults but consider optional "
"functionality and customization options that don\\'t interfere with the "
"primary task."
msgstr ""
"**Bodite prilagodljivi** --- Zagotovite občutljive privzete nastavitve, "
"vendar razmislite o izbirnih funkcijah in možnostih prilagajanja, ki ne "
"ovirajo primarnega opravila."

#: content/hig/_index.md:55
msgid "Note"
msgstr "Opomba"

#: content/hig/_index.md:57
msgid ""
"KDE encourages developing and designing for customization, while providing "
"good default settings. Integrating into other desktop environments is also a "
"virtue, but ultimately we aim for perfection within our own Plasma desktop "
"environment with the default themes and settings. This aim should not be "
"compromised."
msgstr ""
"KDE spodbuja razvoj in načrtovanje za prilagajanje, hkrati pa zagotavlja "
"dobre privzete nastavitve. Integracija v druga namizna okolja je tudi "
"vrlina, na koncu pa si prizadevamo za popolnost znotraj lastnega namiznega "
"okolja Plasma s privzetimi temami in nastavitvami. Ta cilj ne bi smel biti "
"ogrožen."
